7&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/16540674&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcancerres.aacrjournals.org%2Fcgi%2Fcontent%2Ffull%2F66%2F6%2F3222&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Capsaicin"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
